The 3D model files in this directory are third-party assets, each dedicated to
the public domain under CC0 1.0 Universal (see licenses/CREDITS.txt for the
per-file record). CC0 places no restriction on use or redistribution and requires
no attribution; credit is nonetheless given in CREDITS.txt and in the viewer's
info panel.

CC0 1.0 Universal: https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

The scaffolding in this directory (sources.json, make-dinosaur-3d-manifest.mjs,
build-dinosaur-3d.sh, README.md) is part of the ftol-vm-assets project.
